    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all schools give GCSE and A Level students study leave before exams",
        "additional_details": "This should help students be able to concentrate and revise better, by being able to do so at at home rather than in school. Also, many students have more resources to use at home and granting study leave would save students the need to carry text books, notes and other revision materials into school.",
        "background": "The Government should make schools give GCSE and A Level students study leave - time off before their exams - to help them better prepare for their GCSE and A Level exams.",
